## Gelato package environment variables
## Copy to `.env.local` (or `.env`) and adjust.

# Rootstock testnet RPC(s) used by `w3f test` (comma-separated list supported)
PROVIDER_URLS=https://public-node.testnet.rsk.co

# Used by `npx w3f test` (comma-separated RPC URLs; chain id is inferred per URL).
PROVIDER_URLS=https://public-node.testnet.rsk.co
